; Coverage for xact.cc lines 186-190 (account_ends_with_special_char)
; and line 114 (empty name check - covered by the non-empty path)
; When two null-amount postings exist and one account name ends with
; a digit, parenthesis, brace, or bracket, a misspelling warning fires.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Savings 123
    Assets:Cash

test reg -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 9:
Error: Posting with null amount's account may be misspelled:
  "Assets:Savings 123"
end test
